               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary" (fols. 3ra-72va)&#xD;
I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah and hymns (fol. 3ra-7rb)&#xD;
I-2) Introductory exhortation (fols. 7va-8vb)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... “I worship Thee ...” (fols. 8vb-9vb)&#xD;
I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”: 66 miracles (fols. 10ra-72va)&#xD;
I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾǝsi... “Does not the man... ” (distributed among the miracles of Mary, fols. 12rb-18rb, 66rb-68va)&#xD;
II) Taʾāmra Mikāʾel “Miracles of Michael”: 5 miracles (fols. 72vb-76rb)&#xD;
III) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus”: 5 miracles (fols. 76va-80vb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-5.</summary>
