                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The miracles of St Mary (Text I-4) are partly numbered (erroneously). The 1st miracle is followed by a hymn:</note>
                     <note>- Sobä ṣäḥafä Däqsǝyos täʾamriha ʾǝludä ... "When Däqsǝyos wrote the collection of her miracles ..." (<locus target="11va">11va</locus>).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The miracles of Michael (Text II) are followed by ʿarke-hymns.</note>
                  </msItem>
