                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note states that the Ms. was donated to the monastery of Dabra Māryām Säwne. It mentions the name of the donor’s family members but does not reveal the name of the female donor. 
The note is written in the same hand that inserted the name ʿĀmata Māryām into supplication formulas throughout the Ms.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#9vb">f. 9vb</locus>: Testament of wäy[zä]ro Tʿǝbe Kahsay (?)  <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
