                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#81ra">f. 81ra</locus>: Excerpt from the hymn ʾǝsaggǝd la-malakotǝka... “I worship Thy Godhead…”.<quote xml:lang="gez"/>
